5ce11f8891730d5021cc8325cba3307e3f3a152234326376bc7bbb97757bb9e8806d3fdf63280768f9c27533672e72e680ac1a8efccc06b7b4a9478afc3d8c3b  shell-Fix-unsigned-char-promotion-and-truncation.patch
"
